    <h2 id="about">About Us</h2>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-reveal">
        <div class="column">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> Easy Booking</h2>
          <p>
            Book your truck in minutes with our streamlined online platform.
            Select your truck type, choose your dates, and confirm your
            reservation instantly. No hidden fees, no complicated paperwork—just
            fast, transparent booking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-reveal">
        <div class="column">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-headset"></i> 24/7 Availability</h2>
          <p>
            Our customer support team is available around the clock to assist you.
            Whether you need help with your booking, have questions about truck
            features, or require urgent roadside support, we're here 24/7 to help
            you succeed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-reveal">
        <div class="column">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-truck"></i> Wide Range of Trucks</h2>
          <p>
            Choose from our diverse fleet including pickup trucks, box trucks,
            flatbeds, and cargo vans. Each vehicle is meticulously maintained,
            regularly inspected, and equipped with modern safety features to
            ensure a reliable rental experience every time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-reveal">
        <div class="column">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Trusted by Thousands</h2>
          <p>
            Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust TruckRiser for their
            moving, delivery, and logistics needs. Our 4.8-star rating reflects
            our commitment to reliability, transparent pricing, and exceptional
            customer service on every rental.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

